    "originContent": "  <b>Figure 1:</b> The Efficiency Frontier of Instruction Following Datasets. Our proposed method achieves a Win Rate on AlpacaEval 2.0 comparable to MAGPIE while using only 2K synthetic samples (vs. 300K for MAGPIE).",
